API_KEY=# The API key required for authentication (string)
GCS_BUCKET_NAME=# The name of the GCS bucket containing the model and optionally config
GCS_MODEL_PATH=# The path of the model inside the GCS bucket
GCS_CONFIG_URL=# Optional: The path of any custom config file inside the GCS bucket
APP_MAX_BATCH_ITEMS=# Optional: The max number of employee data items provided in a single batch request.
